  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (NC-9 clean)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. COU1 is the validation activity itself — the FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 factors assessed; one factor (Test conditions) achieved level below required due to single test condition. Low confidence in material property inputs is explicitly documented with wide uncertainty bounds; sensitivity analysis confirms stiffness QoI is robust to this uncertainty. Decision Accepted with documented offset rationale.",
